creator: Audron Games
descriptionHtml:
Face the evil little monsters who are snatching vegetables and fruits from the world!

You are the brave Little Luna.The little evil creatures of the land of candy and chocolate are kidnaping the vegatables and the fruits. Go to the land of candy and chocolate and save them. Jump on them, throw stones at their heads with a slingshot and cross beautiful colorful platforms.

Little Luna - Land of Candy Monsters has side scrolls 2d platform game mechanics.

Hope you like the game.
Have fun :)
descriptionShort: Jump on monsters, throw stones and defeat them to save fruits and vegetables.
title: Little Luna - Land of Candy Monsters

creator: Audron Games
descriptionHtml:
Little Luna is smart, fast and brave. Candyland's little monsters are kidnapping and trapping vegetables and fruits. In this fun 2d platform adventure game you will go to the candyland and save your little friends.

Jump on little monsters, throw stones at their heads with a slingshot and cross beautiful colorful platforms with success. Face the little monsters, lollipops cake monsters and complete the platform girl adventure game.

There are also small puzzles in this platform girl adventure game.

Little Luna - Land of Candy Monsters has side scrolls 2d platform adventure game mechanics.

Hope you like the game.
Have fun :)
descriptionShort: Little Luna is a funny 2d platform girl adventure game on the Candyland.
